{
  "stem": "24814.2",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we started seeing bodies lying by the road.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I-- actually, they're just all over-- any old place by the road.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were obviously going to get run over or something.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I got out to just lift one, move it off to the side of the road.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Seemed kind of obscene to let dead bodies lie around.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I couldn't believe-- he had one of these blue and striped-- white, striped outfits on-- prison outfits.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Face-down in the mud.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I turned-- I remember lifting the body, and it was like a child's body.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was a man, a full-grown man.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But I don't suppose he weighed 50 or 60 pounds.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And that face came up out of the mud with the mud dribbling of it, and-- I'll never-- I can see it as if it were yesterday.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "The-- your eyes, you know, have fat around them, so that when you get hit with something, you don't-- it's a cushion of fat.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "The fat was gone, and the eyes were just in this bone sockets-- huge, like the eyes of a bird.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "His face was thin, like a razor.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "The nose was thin like a razor, and the face was just like a skull with brown paint on it.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] The lips were peeled back from the teeth in a snarl, like that, from starvation.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Looked like a scream, just a silent-- I remember thinking, that man's screaming but I can't hear it.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And I lifted him up and put on the side.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And as we went along, we kept moving the bodies off.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Later, we found out what had happened, when their-- our scout cars, which are the advance of a-- of an armored division, [INAUDIBLE] had come up.",
      "word_count": 26
    }
  ],
